These are Puzzles for 4x4 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-4-1::.
Movie-Genre: musical, mystery, action, sports
Transport: helicopter, taxi, trike, boat
Color: ivory, blood-red, yellow, fuchsia
Hobby: singing, traveling, video-games, reading
 1. Transport:helicopter is on the right of Transport:taxi##1
 2. Movie-Genre:musical is in an even position##4
 3. Color:ivory is on the left of Transport:trike##1
 4. Color:yellow is on the right of Movie-Genre:sports##1
 5. Transport:helicopter is on the left or right of Transport:taxi##3
 6. Hobby:singing is on the left of Movie-Genre:mystery##1
 7. Color:blood-red == Movie-Genre:action##1
 8. Hobby:video-games is in an even position##4
 9. Hobby:singing is between Hobby:reading and Transport:boat##2
10. Movie-Genre:musical == Hobby:reading##1
11. Transport:trike == Movie-Genre:sports##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2     |     3      |     4     |
| Movie-Genre          | action  | musical    | sports    | mystery   |
| Transport   | taxi     | helicopter   | trike       | boat    |
| Color   | blood-red | ivory | fuchsia    | yellow |
| Hobby           | traveling | reading       | singing | video-games     |

